      <item>
        <title>New tour</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/matlab/sparsity_9b_music/&quot;&gt;This tour explores&lt;/a&gt; the use of the MUSIC algortithm to perform sparse spikes deconvolution. The localization of the spikes is obtained by finding the root of a polynomial.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
